      <p style="color:var(--ink-muted); font-size:var(--fs-body-lg); margin: var(--space-4) auto var(--space-6);">{{ ctaCopy or "We'll cover what's draining your week, where the leverage is, and whether we're a fit. No pitch. No obligation." }}</p>
